      "role": "user",
      "content": "i’ve been wandering through these cities for weeks now, seeing all the things i thought i needed to see. but honestly... the itinerary feels empty. it's like i've reached the final stop on the map and there's just nothing left to explore. i feel like i've seen enough of the world.",
